  <feedback condition="$numerical">Enter <m>\pi</m> if needed in your answer; do not round. Your answer should be an integer or an exact rational number, not a decimal approximation.</feedback>

  <feedback condition="$notSimple">Remember to simplify your answer. See <ref uri="https://openstax.org/books/prealgebra-2e/pages/4-2-multiply-and-divide-fractions">this</ref> online textbook chapter, or <ref uri="https://open.lib.umn.edu/algebra/chapter/topic-1-3-reducing-fractions/">this</ref> video lesson for a refresher on simplifying fractions.</feedback>
  
